{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"660f0ef2b7","title":"为阅看《关于（三国演义》》前两部分给林克的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a52a363043","index":0,"year":1959,"month":4,"day":24,"articleId":"660f0ef2b7"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"ae84d49c13","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"660f0ef2b7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林克，当时任毛泽东办公室秋书。"},{"id":"f4f16bbd58","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"660f0ef2b7","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在1959年4月23日《北京晚报》第三版上，该版登载了吴组细摆写的《关于（三国演义）》（三），主要是就《三国演义》来谈历史和文艺的关系。文章认为，《三国演义》以“拥刘反曹”为总的倾尚，把刘备和曹操处理成矛盾对立的双方。不能表面地认为这只是反映了统治者内部的矛盾，那是历史：作为文艺作品，它实质上还反映了封建时代广大被压迫人民跟统治势力的矛盾，反映了黑暗时代人民群众的民主要求和爱国思想。在这里，文艺和历史必须区别开来，不能因为“拥刘反曹”的倾向有正统历史观，就否定它的民主思想。"},{"id":"444ce0709e","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"660f0ef2b7","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《关于（三国演义）》（一）（二）分别载于1959年4月9日和15日《北京晚报》第三版。1959年5月13日，《北京晚报》又连载了《关于（三国演义》》（四）。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7b72c53ad4","type":"title","text":"为阅看《关于（三国演义》》前两部分给林克的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"660f0ef2b7"},{"id":"ae84d49c13","type":"paragraph","text":"林克：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"660f0ef2b7"},{"id":"f4f16bbd58","type":"paragraph","text":"请你替我找《关于（三国演义》》的（一）（二）两节，我想看一看。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"660f0ef2b7"},{"id":"444ce0709e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"660f0ef2b7"},{"id":"ae0f2ef8f4","type":"paragraph","text":"四月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"660f0ef2b7"}],"page":{"id":"345eb93fb7","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"660f0ef2b7","start":464,"end":464}}}},"__N_SSG":true}